# Dash dashboard

- Build the single-page UI in `app/dashboard.py` (hero, chart, stat rail, supporting cards).
- Use Mantine components and `dcc.Graph` with colors from `app/components/theme.py` / `assets/theme.css`.
- Keep fetch and metric math out of layout helpers where possible (`app/metrics.py`, `app/data/bitcoin_client.py`).
